    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hmmm, indeed I've managed to reproduce it. The bug is not in that line of code, it's a side effect of using the query itself as an iterator. When we reach the root of the chain, the parent of the genesis block is the nil hash, which is interpreted in a special way in the code. I guess we haven't caught this issue because we don't use this type of queries currently in the code. Let me see how to cleanly solve this.\n",
